---
layout: layouts/inner.njk
title: Products
permalink: /products/
eyebrow:
  en: Our Products
  vi: Sản phẩm
  zh: 产品
heading:
  en: Nutrition Designed for Every Stage.
  vi: Giải pháp dinh dưỡng cho mọi giai đoạn.
  zh: 为每个阶段设计的营养方案。
lead:
  en: From pig and poultry feed to aquaculture and specialty nutrition, our products are developed through scientific research.
  vi: Mỗi dòng sản phẩm được phát triển dựa trên nghiên cứu khoa học nhằm tối ưu sức khỏe vật nuôi.
  zh: 从猪禽饲料到水产与特种营养，产品均基于科学研究开发。
---

<div class="products__grid products__grid--page">
  {% for product in collections.products %}
  <a href="{{ product.url | url }}" class="pcard" style="--pc:{{ product.data.color }}">
    <span class="pcard__code">{{ product.data.code }}</span>
    <span class="pcard__name">
      <span class="lang en">{{ product.data.title.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ product.data.title.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ product.data.title.zh }}</span>
    </span>
    <span class="pcard__arrow">→</span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
<p style="margin-top:2rem">
  <a class="btn btn--dark" href="{{ '/downloads/' | url }}">
    <span class="lang en">Download catalog</span>
    <span class="lang vi">Tải catalogue</span>
    <span class="lang zh">下载产品目录</span>
  </a>
</p>
